00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:51,040
I'm not going anywhere.

536
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:06,280
Alright, alright, that's enough, Carlo.

537
00:31:06,280 --> 00:31:07,480
There's no rush. Let me handle this.

538
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:09,480
You don't need to worry about this, just go.

539
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:14,380
Let me tell you, I'm taking the keys
and opening the door right now.

540
00:31:14,380 --> 00:31:16,980
Just you wait, I'll take you straight
to the police station.

541
00:31:16,980 --> 00:31:18,432
Or should we try again?

542
00:31:18,432 --> 00:31:19,520
Try again?

543
00:31:19,520 --> 00:31:20,640
He could run away from home.

544
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:21,640
He's already run away.

545
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,760
He must have his reasons.

546
00:31:22,760 --> 00:31:24,040
If we forcibly take him back,

547
00:31:24,040 --> 00:31:25,320
what if he runs away again?

548
00:31:25,320 --> 00:31:27,400
If it really doesn't work,
we will carry him to the police station.

549
00:31:28,520 --> 00:31:29,540
Alright then.

550
00:31:29,540 --> 00:31:31,200
I think what you said makes sense.

551
00:31:31,200 --> 00:31:32,360
Or else,

552
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:34,400
let's eat something first.

553
00:31:38,432 --> 00:31:39,760
I have a plan now.

554
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:52,360
What are you preparing to cook?

555
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:54,592
Banana pancakes.

556
00:31:54,592 --> 00:31:55,760
Sweets.

557
00:31:55,760 --> 00:31:58,280
Definitely. All kids like sweets, don't they?

558
00:31:58,800 --> 00:32:00,280
Wave it under his nose.

559
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:01,320
Get him to crave it so that he will come out.

560
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:02,600
But if he doesn't crave it,

561
00:32:02,600 --> 00:32:04,520
to tell the truth, I may just
have to find the keys then.

562
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:19,720
You're pretty good at this.

563
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:21,640
Not too bad. Well,

564
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:23,360
not worse than Shen Chen, am I?

565
00:32:24,352 --> 00:32:25,696
You men are really funny.

566
00:32:25,696 --> 00:32:26,720
How about this?

567
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:27,760
Someday at Tianlin Hospital,

568
00:32:27,760 --> 00:32:29,120
let's organize a cooking contest for you.

569
00:32:29,120 --> 00:32:31,000
You can have a competition
and see who is better.

570
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:34,280
I don't have the time for that.

571
00:32:46,432 --> 00:32:48,224
<i>The fourth rule of secret love.</i>

572
00:32:48,224 --> 00:32:50,680
<i>He is willing to cook for you.</i>

573
00:32:51,800 --> 00:32:52,960
Carlo, let's go.

574
00:33:07,072 --> 00:33:09,200
Kid, you're probably hungry, aren't you?

575
00:33:09,856 --> 00:33:11,808
The gentleman and I made you
something good to eat.

576
00:33:11,808 --> 00:33:13,280
Would you like to come out and eat some?

577
00:33:13,280 --> 00:33:14,464
I'm not hungry.

578
00:33:14,464 --> 00:33:16,480
Your kitten was eating so well just now.

579
00:33:16,480 --> 00:33:17,720
You must be hungry, too.

580
00:33:19,040 --> 00:33:20,040
Let me tell you,

581
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:22,720
I advise you to give up resistance now.

582
00:33:23,552 --> 00:33:25,568
Isn't it okay to come out and have a good meal?

583
00:33:25,568 --> 00:33:27,280
You can feel a little better.

584
00:33:27,280 --> 00:33:29,360
And don't make me so angry, okay?

585
00:33:29,360 --> 00:33:30,432
Even if I'm hungry, I won't eat.

586
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:32,360
You both definitely want to trick me out.

587
00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:33,600
Then take me to the police station.

588
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:39,640
We didn't lie to you.

589
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:41,440
We absolutely will not
take you to the police station.

590
00:33:41,440 --> 00:33:43,320
I won't, under circumstances you're unwilling,

591
00:33:43,320 --> 00:33:45,400
call your parents, okay?

592
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:50,640
I don't believe. What if you cheat?

593
00:33:50,640 --> 00:33:51,744
If we cheat you,

594
00:33:51,744 --> 00:33:53,760
just let the gentleman's house
explode in place.

595
00:33:53,760 --> 00:33:56,160
- Leaving us nowhere to live.
<i>- Explode in place.</i>

596
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:58,640
<i>Why are you looking at me?
Am I not coaxing a child?</i>

597
00:33:58,640 --> 00:34:01,440
<i>Woman, what are you swearing at?</i>

598
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:30,120
Are you full?

599
00:34:38,880 --> 00:34:41,840
You are not full. Just say it.

600
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:43,120
It's not like we won't feed you.

601
00:34:43,936 --> 00:34:44,960
Eat up.

602
00:34:45,639 --> 00:34:46,880
Thank you, uncle.

603
00:34:47,520 --> 00:34:48,679
Don't. Don't.

604
00:34:51,456 --> 00:34:52,840
Kid,

605
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:55,239
you haven't told me what your name is.

606
00:35:00,224 --> 00:35:01,800
I'm asking you a question.

607
00:35:02,528 --> 00:35:03,552
What's wrong?

608
00:35:04,200 --> 00:35:07,080
Your parents won't let you tell strangers
about your family situation?

609
00:35:10,080 --> 00:35:11,880
Your parents are right.

610
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:13,920
But we are not strangers.

611
00:35:15,744 --> 00:35:16,768
Look,

612
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:19,840
we have known each other for so long.

613
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:22,280
By now, we definitely can't
be considered strangers.

614
00:35:23,520 --> 00:35:25,920
Miss, my name is Feifei.

615
00:35:30,240 --> 00:35:31,260
Feifei,

616
00:35:31,260 --> 00:35:33,280
where do you live?

617
00:35:34,208 --> 00:35:35,328
I'm full.

618
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:40,000
What's wrong with you?
We're talking to you. Why are you…?

619
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:43,600
Breaking through psychological defenses
is not so easy.

620
00:35:43,600 --> 00:35:44,840
We have to take it slow.

621
00:35:47,000 --> 00:35:48,800
Okay, your turn.

622
00:36:01,184 --> 00:36:02,420
Feifei,

623
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:04,600
