624
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:06,240
Let's three play together.

625
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:10,260
One phone, three people, how to play?

626
00:36:10,260 --> 00:36:12,920
Who told you we have to play mobile games?

627
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:20,760
Why you're not throwing quickly?

628
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:22,960
Why are you in such a hurry?
Just roll a five directly.

629
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:24,360
Kill you in seconds.

630
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:28,840
Oh my god, that's miraculous!

631
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:33,280
See, it's just that miraculous!

632
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:35,440
No need to play, one, two, three, four, five.

633
00:36:38,176 --> 00:36:39,200
No need to play.

634
00:36:39,720 --> 00:36:41,000
Well,

635
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:43,400
I don't believe it, let's play another round.

636
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:45,040
Miss,

637
00:36:45,040 --> 00:36:46,976
