638
00:36:46,976 --> 00:36:48,120
It's not my problem.

639
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:49,520
It's a problem of my luck.

640
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:51,104
This flying chess game depends on luck.

641
00:36:51,104 --> 00:36:52,200
He's just lucky.

642
00:36:53,728 --> 00:36:55,776
Flying chess not only involves luck.

643
00:36:55,776 --> 00:36:57,280
It also requires strategy.

644
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,980
There's even strategy?

645
00:36:58,980 --> 00:37:01,320
Luck is just a part of strength.

646
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:03,440
You're really not suited to this game.

647
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:10,480
When did you two become a team?

648
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:12,500
Okay, I'm not suited for this game, right?

649
00:37:12,500 --> 00:37:14,200
But I'm good at another game.

650
00:37:14,200 --> 00:37:16,640
Why don't we compete in dancing?

651
00:37:16,640 --> 00:37:17,728
How do we compete?

652
00:37:21,200 --> 00:37:23,080
Don't we have any normal dances?

653
00:37:23,080 --> 00:37:24,720
Do we have to do this?

654
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,960
Wait, you both have a star.

655
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,480
Why don't I have one?

656
00:37:28,480 --> 00:37:30,200
You didn't even dance.

657
00:37:30,200 --> 00:37:31,680
But, I was dancing.

658
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:38,880
The uncle ruined our rhythm.

659
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:40,640
Who are you calling uncle?

660
00:37:40,640 --> 00:37:42,020
Then are you admitting defeat?

661
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:43,380
I admit defeat.

662
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:45,780
As an uncle, I definitely admit defeat.

663
00:37:45,780 --> 00:37:46,820
Now,

664
00:37:46,820 --> 00:37:49,520
we invite the two of you
for a championship match, okay?

665
00:37:49,520 --> 00:37:50,760
I will play the music for you guys.

666
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:52,920
You two, are you alright
with a championship duel?

667
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,080
- Okay.
- Come on.

668
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:57,540
Are you ready?

669
00:37:57,540 --> 00:37:58,592
Let's do this.

670
00:38:15,488 --> 00:38:17,632
Feifei, what's wrong?

671
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:24,920
This dance is easy to dance.

672
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:26,200
The song is also nice.

673
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:28,940
When I was little,

674
00:38:28,940 --> 00:38:30,480
my mom used to sing this song for me.

675
00:38:38,624 --> 00:38:40,880
Are you missing your mom?

676
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:41,952
No.

677
00:38:48,360 --> 00:38:50,000
<i>Feifei, you are about to be late,
you are about to be late.</i>

678
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:52,540
<i>Come on, come on, hurry, hurry. Come on.</i>

679
00:38:52,540 --> 00:38:54,080
<i>Dad is here to pick you up after school.</i>

680
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:56,400
<i>What happened?</i>

681
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:57,960
<i>Dad, I forgot my backpack.</i>

682
00:38:58,480 --> 00:39:00,480
<i>Don't you carry it yourself?</i>

683
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:02,840
<i>No, mom usually helps me with it.</i>

684
00:39:03,400 --> 00:39:06,016
<i>What can I do? All my books are in the bag.</i>

685
00:39:06,016 --> 00:39:07,160
<i>How am I going to attend class?</i>

686
00:39:07,160 --> 00:39:08,440
<i>Feifei, in that case,</i>

687
00:39:08,440 --> 00:39:09,600
<i>you go to class first for today.</i>

688
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:11,800
<i>I'm going to be late.</i>

689
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:13,660
<i>I will call your teacher later to explain.</i>

690
00:39:13,660 --> 00:39:15,168
<i>Go, hurry up, hurry up. Go to class.</i>

691
00:39:15,168 --> 00:39:16,240
<i>Be good in class.</i>

692
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:18,560
<i>Dad, Daddy.</i>

693
00:39:18,560 --> 00:39:22,000
- <i>♪ Twinkle, twinkle, little star ♪</i>
- <i>Mom, Mom.</i>

694
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,360
<i>Can you play with me for a while?</i>

695
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:26,640
<i>Feifei, you play with your phone for a while.</i>

696
00:39:26,640 --> 00:39:28,320
<i>Mom is giving prenatal education to the baby.</i>

697
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:32,440
<i>♪ Twinkle, twinkle, little star ♪</i>

698
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:35,880
- <i>♪ It fills up the whole sky ♪</i>
- <i>Mummy,</i>

699
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:38,380
<i>isn't this the song you sang to me
when I was little?</i>

700
00:39:38,380 --> 00:39:41,080
<i>Yes, now Mom has to sing it
for the little baby.</i>

701
00:39:47,760 --> 00:39:49,800
<i>Daddy, I have finished my homework.</i>

702
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:51,240
<i>Can you take me to play basketball?</i>

703
00:39:51,240 --> 00:39:53,380
<i>Daddy has to buy wonton for Mommy.</i>

704
00:39:53,380 --> 00:39:55,240
<i>Play with Blue, good boy.</i>

705
00:39:55,240 --> 00:39:56,800
<i>But you promised me.</i>

706
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:01,800
<i>Feifei, Mom vomited out all the dinner she ate.</i>

707
00:40:02,520 --> 00:40:04,040
<i>If she doesn't eat anything,</i>

708
00:40:04,040 --> 00:40:06,040
<i>how is the baby in her womb
going to get the nutrition?</i>

709
00:40:06,040 --> 00:40:08,760
<i>It will then be born skinny and tiny, won't it?</i>

710
00:40:09,680 --> 00:40:11,900
<i>You can watch TV
or play on your phone for a while.</i>

711
00:40:11,900 --> 00:40:14,560
<i>But whatever you do, don't disturb Mom.</i>

712
00:40:14,560 --> 00:40:15,680
<i>She just fell asleep.</i>

713
00:40:16,360 --> 00:40:17,472
<i>Be good.</i>

714
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:29,640
<i>Blue, it's just us two left again.</i>

715
00:40:31,104 --> 00:40:32,160
<i>Goodbye.</i>

716
00:40:32,160 --> 00:40:33,472
<i>Goodbye.</i>

717
00:40:33,472 --> 00:40:36,280
<i>Feifei, who is picking you up today?</i>

718
00:40:37,792 --> 00:40:38,840
<i>Don't worry.</i>

719
00:40:38,840 --> 00:40:40,880
<i>I guess your parents will be here soon.</i>

720
00:40:43,520 --> 00:40:45,080
<i>Your dad is calling.</i>

721
00:40:46,520 --> 00:40:47,800
<i>Feifei's father,</i>

722
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,960
<i>who of you is picking up Feifei today?</i>

723
00:40:51,640 --> 00:40:54,600
<i>Okay, then I will talk to him, okay.</i>

724
00:40:55,424 --> 00:40:56,600
<i>Feifei,</i>

725
00:40:56,600 --> 00:40:59,180
<i>your dad is taking your mom
to the hospital for a checkup.</i>

726
00:40:59,180 --> 00:41:00,640
<i>It might be a bit late.</i>

727
00:41:00,640 --> 00:41:01,920
<i>Let's go back to class first.</i>

728
00:41:08,920 --> 00:41:12,720
<i>♪ Twinkle, twinkle, little star ♪</i>

729
00:41:12,720 --> 00:41:15,740
- <i>Feifei, you take Blue out first.</i>
- <i>♪ It fills up the whole sky ♪</i>

730
00:41:15,740 --> 00:41:17,200
<i>I have something to say to Mom.</i>

731
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:19,840
<i>Go out quickly.</i>

732
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:28,100
<i>This second one really gives you a hard time.</i>

733
00:41:28,100 --> 00:41:30,000
<i>It's tougher than when you
were carrying our first.</i>

734
00:41:31,520 --> 00:41:32,720
<i>Let me check your ringworm.</i>

735
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,600
<i>Progressively itchier.</i>

736
00:41:37,600 --> 00:41:39,920
<i>It's been a few days,
why is it still like this?</i>

737
00:41:39,920 --> 00:41:41,760
<i>Yes, being pregnant,</i>

738
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:43,180
<i>I dare not apply any medication.</i>

739
00:41:43,180 --> 00:41:44,580
<i>What should I do?</i>

740
00:41:44,580 --> 00:41:45,960
<i>Let me show you a photo.</i>

741
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:50,160
<i>Do you think it looks like this?</i>

742
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:53,408
<i>It does.</i>

743
00:41:53,408 --> 00:41:54,480
<i>My God.</i>

744
00:41:55,440 --> 00:41:56,480
<i>What is this?</i>

745
00:41:57,320 --> 00:41:59,260
<i>Ringworm from a cat.</i>

746
00:41:59,260 --> 00:42:00,680
<i>What should we do about this?</i>

747
00:42:00,680 --> 00:42:01,760
<i>Calm yourself first.</i>

748
00:42:04,240 --> 00:42:06,520
<i>A few days ago, I asked my colleagues
who have cats.</i>

749
00:42:07,080 --> 00:42:08,600
<i>When their wives were pregnant,</i>

750
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:09,900
<i>they all sent their cats away.</i>

751
00:42:09,900 --> 00:42:11,760
<i>Saying they were afraid of getting infected.</i>

752
00:42:13,160 --> 00:42:15,920
<i>If it's not a miscarriage,
it will be a malformed fetus.</i>

753
00:42:15,920 --> 00:42:17,280
<i>Is it that serious?</i>

754
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,420
<i>What should we do?</i>

755
00:42:20,420 --> 00:42:22,960
<i>Why don't we send Blue away first?</i>

756
00:42:24,040 --> 00:42:25,680
<i>No, no.</i>

757
00:42:26,240 --> 00:42:29,180
<i>Blue grew up with Feifei.</i>

758
00:42:29,180 --> 00:42:30,680
<i>Feifei will definitely not want to let it go.</i>

759
00:42:30,680 --> 00:42:32,160
<i>What can we do then?</i>

760
00:42:32,160 --> 00:42:34,480
<i>- No, no.
- Now, the baby in your womb is most important.</i>

761
00:42:35,480 --> 00:42:37,000
<i>He will definitely understand us in the future.</i>

762
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:48,000
Feifei, how nice would it be
to have another child at home.

763
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:49,280
He can play with you.

764
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,680
You won't feel lonely then.

765
00:42:50,680 --> 00:42:52,680
Not good, not good at all.

